      "settings": {
        "content": "<p><strong>Best Wall Decor & Home Decor Items, Delivered Across India - Dekorvibe</strong></p><p>Your home says a lot about you, and every piece of decor you choose adds a little personality to your space. At Dekorvibe, we offer a wide collection of <strong>home decor items</strong> that help you build a space that feels calm, creative, and completely yours. From wall art to furniture, we bring you pieces that look good and feel right at home.</p><p>Whether you're setting up a new house or simply changing a few corners, our carefully selected products can make a big difference. Browse through our unique range of <a href=\"#\">wall painting</a>, handcrafted <a href=\"#\">mandir</a>, soft lighting solutions like <a href=\"#\">lamp</a>, elegant <a href=\"#\">mirror</a>, or space-saving <a href=\"#\">tables</a> and <a href=\"#\">chairs</a>  each one designed to make your space more meaningful.</p><p>With easy online access and delivery across India, decorating your home is now just a few clicks away.</p><p><strong>Choose From a Wide Range of Home Decor Categories</strong></p><p>Dekorvibe makes it easy to shop for your entire home. Our categories are built to suit different tastes and needs, making it simple to find items that match your style and space.</p><p><strong>Wall Art and Paintings</strong></p><p>Browse our <a href=\"#\">Wall Paintings</a> collection to add color and expression to your rooms. From abstract and modern designs to traditional themes, we have pieces that speak to every mood. Looking for something spiritual? Our Radha Krishna Paintings are ideal for prayer areas or quiet corners.</p><p><strong>Mirrors</strong></p><p>Our <a href=\"#\">Mirrors</a> combine function with style. Use them to brighten up small rooms, reflect natural light, or simply add a designer touch to walls and entrances.</p><p><strong>Lamps and Lighting</strong></p><p>Set the mood with our <a href=\"#\">Lamps</a>. Choose from table lamps, wall lights, or decorative